OL,6,F"They are putting fear in people who
OL,7,Fare scared to speak up.
OL,9,F"I don't find it normal in this
OL,10,Fcivilised society for such racism
OL,11,Fgoing on."
OL,13,FLocal politician, Deputy Beatriz
OL,14,FPoree, believes the treatment of some
OL,15,Foverseas temporary workers in Jersey
OL,16,Fis unacceptable.
