OL,6,FShe is calling for a modern slavery
OL,7,Flaw to be introduced, as exists in the
OL,8,FUK, given that there is currently no
OL,9,Flegal protection for these employees
OL,10,Facross the Channel Islands.
OL,12,FShe adds: "Exploitation takes place
OL,13,Fwhen people are made to feel secondary
OL,14,Fto a business, the financial gain
OL,15,Fbecomes more important than people's
OL,16,Fwelfare.
OL,18,F"Health concerns can come to a point
OL,19,Fwhere you worry for the safety and the
OL,20,Fwell-being of that particular worker.
