OL,6,F"In extreme cases, people have taken
OL,7,Ftheir lives."
OL,9,FITV News has spoken to a
OL,10,Frepresentative for migrant workers in
OL,11,FJersey who alleges exploitation,
OL,12,Fincluding forced working hours,
OL,13,Fpayment delays, and harassment.
OL,15,FIn 2024, 2,432 permits were issued to
OL,16,Fpeople coming to work temporarily in
OL,17,FJersey, a figure which has more than
OL,18,Fdoubled since 2021.
