OL,7,Fto work in the hospitality sector, but
OL,8,Falso agriculture, construction and
OL,9,Ffishing.
OL,11,FSome companies across the islands have
OL,12,Ftheir own anti-modern slavery policies
OL,13,Fto protect workers, but these are not
OL,14,Fsupported by law.
