OL,6,FNigel Godfrey, Operations Director of
OL,7,Fthe pub and restaurant chain Randalls
OL,8,Fin Jersey, says: "It's down to the
OL,9,Femployer to ensure that the employee
OL,10,Fis OK when they come here and I think
OL,11,Fthe Government may need to get more
OL,12,Finvolved with getting feedback from
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,F"Migrant workers have been an absolute
OL,16,Fsaving grace ... without them, we
OL,17,Fwouldn't be able to trade."
