OL,6,FIn 2015, the UK introduced a sweeping
OL,7,Flaw which covers slavery, forced or
OL,8,Fcompulsory labour and carries a
OL,9,Fmaximum sentence of life imprisonment.
OL,11,FDeputy Mary Le Hegarat, Jersey's
OL,12,FJustice and Home Affairs Minister,
OL,13,Fsays: "Looking at the important issue
OL,14,Fof modern slavery is a priority for
OL,15,Fme, and remains so, but this has had
OL,16,Fto be balanced against resources and
OL,17,Fprogress achieved in the ongoing work
OL,18,Fmy department leads on violence
OL,19,Fagainst women and girls, which is a
OL,20,Fcompeting priority in my portfolio."
