OL,6,F"The Jersey Customs and Immigration
OL,7,FService (JCIS) keep the Work Permit
OL,8,FPolicy under constant review and
OL,9,Fengage with key stakeholders to ensure
OL,10,Fthe policy is fit for purpose.
OL,12,F"Part of this work provides for
OL,13,Fprotection in respect of modern
OL,14,Fslavery and exploitation, and this is
OL,15,Fan ongoing key focus for JCIS."
OL,17,FIn January, a farm worker died after a
OL,18,Ffire engulfed the cabin he was living
OL,19,Fin and his family have since raised
OL,20,Fconcerns about the standard of his
OL,21,Faccommodation.
